ygData.messageBody:
Yeah, the boss of the LAN shop is guild member, so members got their
previlidges ;P Somemore sometime got jude female guild members who visite
the shop and chat with u ;P

Innoruuk AdV is going pretty strong....can send me a tell also if u are
coming to Innoruuk. May not be able to give u very solid loots but
definitely can give u stuffs better than u yaself farm it b4 lvl 20 ;) Err
this only saying for myself coz I'm kinda dry after helping a few sg
players and few UO guild members (Baja shard, The Dark Wardens) who come
over to EQ; I guess others got much better stuffs to offer ;)


Ziltus Planeswalker (AdV) Innoruuk, de Ass Zapper

p/s1: Ah, how I missed this kinda of earn-money msg 2 yrs ago....
p/s2: If u come to Inno, pls dun use the name frostburn anymore, coz we got
a pet bear in guild also named Frostburn, heh.
